name: ILOVEFOXCONN: The Virtual Tour (Canceled)
blurb: ILOVEFOXCONN is an interactive mockumentary/touch game exploring the impact of western and state capitalism on our morality.

rewards.reward: By pledging 1 dollar or more, you'll get a copy of ILOVEFOXCONN in your flavor of platform (ios or 2.2+android device), the satisfaction that you've helped create something that hasn't been tried before and Terrys gratitude!

By pledging 10 dollars or more, you'll get your name in a bright lights in the benefactors section of ILOVEFOXCONN, the EP of ILOVEFOXCONNs soundtrack consisting of 5 culturally inspired tracks from the game, the satisfaction that you've helped push the limits of interactive media and Terrys heartfelt gratitude!

By pledging 25 dollars or more, you'll get your name as a blue light special in the benefactors section of ILOVEFOXCONN, an official reproduction ILOVEFOXCONN game tshirt with button to show your support of the man who makes your iphone, the satisfaction that you continually do your part to push the global economy forward and Terrys sincerest gratitude!

By pledging 50 dollars or more, you get your name in heavenly lights in the benefactors section of the game, a wall scroll of "The Tao of Goo", Terry Goo's 9 point business philosophy to motivate you on a daily basis, the satisfaction that you're an enlightened individual who can rattle off the perfect quote for any given situation, and Terrys deepest gratitude!

By pledging 100 dollars or more, you get your name in stars in the benefactors section of the game, an official ILOVEFOXCONN silicone case for i-phone4, ipad-1 (or ipad2 if avail), i-pod4 or droid, an extra official ILOVEFOXCONN replica shirt and button in pink or limited edition blue, and the satisfaction that you ARE the one who made this possible and you don't need to prove it by showing off all your swag and Terrys sincerest and deepest heartfelt gratitude.

A pledge this large deserves special recognition. Your name is diamond encrusted, in ethereal glory in the platinum members benefactors section of the game, 2 official ILOVEFOXCONN womens briefs or mens boxer shorts, a set of ILOVEFOXCONN pillowcases, and you get to be personally represented as one of the workers toiling away within the game and as a named game achievement. A donation this large will help you sleep at night and, of course, you will have Terrys eternal gratitude!
